description:
The Schick Hydro Silk Refill blades feature a Hydra-Boost serum formulated with shea butter and sea minerals to hydrate* while you shave.It's 5-curve sensing blades to give you incredible closeness, while following the natural shape of your body. The cartridge is perfect for accessing hard-to reach areas, and each blade includes unique skin guards to smooth skin and help prevent irritation.*Moisturises up to 2 hours after shaving

The Schick Hydro Silk Refill blades feature a Hydra-Boost serum formulated with shea butter and sea minerals. It's 5-curve sensing blades to give you incredible closeness, while following the natural shape of your body. The cartridge is perfect for accessing hard-to reach areas, and each blade includes unique skin guards to smooth skin and help prevent irritation.

Use with either the Schick Hydro Silk Razor or Hydro Silk Trimstyle handles.

*Moisturises up to 2 hours after shaving

5 Curve Sensing blades for our closest shave

Hydra-Boost Serum hydrates* & protects from irritation for our smoothest glide *Moisturises for up to 2 hours after shaving

With a touch if Shea Butter and sea minerals

Designed to give you control over your shave
